# Optional: add ONE extra self-hosted GitLab instance to LOCAL builds.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (gitignored) and set both variables to whole
# match patterns — Plasmo substitutes them into host_permissions and the
# content-script matches at build time; when unset, the entries are dropped,
# so public/Store builds contain gitlab.com only.
#
# IMPORTANT: keep the whole-string "$VAR" form in package.json and
# src/contents/gitlab-mr.tsx. Interpolated forms like "$VAR/*" are NOT
# dropped when the variable is unset and would leave an invalid literal
# match pattern in the manifest.
#
# PLASMO_EXTRA_GITLAB_HOST_PERMISSION=https://gitlab.example.com/*
# PLASMO_EXTRA_GITLAB_MR_MATCH=https://gitlab.example.com/*/-/merge_requests/*
